}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== *Product Model: SDGOB-0892 :Part Number:{{HP PN|1150-7935}} (Straight Connector) :Part Number:{{HP PN|1150-7936}} (Right Angle Connector)
*This module widely used in HP wireless-enabled printers.
*The ''Marvell'' logo and "3-10740-XX AX5" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. *The ''Marvell'' logo and "HP8786U AX5" seems to be silkscreened on (most?) production units.
Different manufacturers were likely used for this wireless module.. *[[AzureWave AW-GM310S]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7935}}) :HP C4780/C4795 ([https://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=9SIAAD046B4565 Newegg]) OUI: 74:F0:6D *[[Foxconn U98H063.00]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7938}}) ([http://www.laserxperts.com/1150-7938.html label]) *[[Foxconn U98H063.06]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7938}}) ([https://storage.googleapis.com/images.nevod.net/hash/2479cd5c4aebec071ce306790fc9a6b2.full.jpg label]) :HP LaserJet CM1410/CM1415/M375/M475 *[[Foxconn U98H063.01]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7940}}) ([http://www.laserxperts.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/1/1150-7940_2.jpg label]) *[[Foxconn U98H063.07]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7937}} /{{HP PN|1150-7940}}) ([https://scanner.com.ru/wa-data/public/shop/products/91/08/1780891/images/16715/16715.970.jpg label]) :HP LJ CP1525/M175/M275/M251/M276/M351/M401/M425/M451 *[[Foxconn U98H074.00]] (HP PN:{{HP PN|1150-7946}}) ([https://wikidevi.com/wiki/File:SDGOB-0892_top.jpg label]) :HP OfficeJet 6100/8500A/8600 "U98H063 GP" and "800505 v025" is silkscreened on the board.
